Attendance Management System

Project Overview

The Attendance Management System is a web-based application developed to simplify and automate the attendance process in educational institutions. It enables administrators and faculty members to manage student records, record attendance, and generate attendance reports efficiently. The system reduces manual errors, saves time, and provides accurate attendance statistics.

Project Objectives

Automate student attendance management.

Reduce paperwork and manual calculations.

Maintain accurate attendance records.

Generate attendance reports and percentage.

Improve efficiency in educational institutions.


